OL,3,CDebt-ridden couple hid from bailiffs
OL,4,Cafter firm collapsed
OL,6,FA self-employed couple who racked up
OL,7,F#65,000 of debt after their
OL,8,Fconstruction firm collapsed are urging
OL,9,Fothers with money worries to seek help.
OL,11,FSam and Paul Helsby's company, based
OL,12,Fin, went bust last year after the war
OL,13,Fin Ukraine saw their costs soar and
OL,14,Fleft customers unable to meet the
OL,15,Fprice increases.
OL,17,FMr Helsby, 45, who had been a joiner
OL,18,Ffor 24 years, began taking on more of
OL,19,Fthe workload to save on contractors'
OL,20,Ffees but in September last year he had
OL,21,Fa stroke.
