OL,6,FHe lost the ability to speak, along
OL,7,Fwith all feeling in the right side of
OL,8,Fhis body for 12 weeks, leaving him
OL,9,Funable to work as the bills continued
OL,10,Fto pile up.
OL,12,FWife Sam, who did the administration
OL,13,Fwork for the business, said: "Paul had
OL,14,Fthe stroke in September and by
OL,15,FNovember we had got bailiffs coming.
OL,17,F"Really quickly we couldn't answer the
OL,18,Fdoor any more and they sit outside for
OL,19,Fages. You feel a bit like a prisoner
OL,20,Fin your own home."
