OL,3,CDebt-ridden couple hid from bailiffs
OL,4,Cafter firm collapsed
OL,6,FIn a bid to dig themselves out of
OL,7,Fdebt, the couple borrowed money from
OL,8,Ftheir children, handed back their
OL,9,Fphones and cars and used food parcels.
OL,11,FThey contacted the Christians Against
OL,12,FPoverty (CAP) charity for free debt
OL,13,Fadvice in December and Paul declared
OL,14,Fhimself bankrupt in March.
OL,16,FPaul said: "CAP saved our lives. I was
OL,17,Fdone with everything. It saved our
OL,18,Fmarriage - I could've called quits on
OL,19,Feverything at one point.
