OL,6,F"For us it's made me stand up again
OL,7,Fand say, 'well alright it failed but
OL,8,FI'm still here'."
OL,10,FThe charity unveiled its annual client
OL,11,Freport, which surveyed many of those
OL,12,Fthey have supported, at a conference
OL,13,Fin Leeds.
OL,15,FThe report found that low income was
OL,16,Fthe main contributor of debt, while
OL,17,Fstating that two years of rising costs
OL,18,Fhave left many households "trapped
OL,19,Funder the rubble of debt and poverty".
