OL,6,FMeanwhile new figures show that
OL,7,Finflation slowed to 2.3 percent in
OL,8,FApril having hit 9.6 percent in
OL,9,FOctober 2022.
OL,11,FStewart McCulloch, CAP's chief
OL,12,Fexecutive, said: "The average person
OL,13,Fbuying the average things is going to
OL,14,Fstart feeling relief now and the cost
OL,15,Fof living crisis ending but we don't
OL,16,Fdeal with the average person. The
OL,17,Faverage income of a CAP client is half
OL,18,Fthe average and 60 percent are below
OL,19,Fthe poverty line.
