OL,6,F"Those who are struggling are
OL,7,Fstruggling more, those who are under
OL,8,Fwater remain under water and that's
OL,9,Fwhat we're seeing on the ground."
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,12,FWork and Pensions said the Government
OL,13,Fprevented 1.3 million people falling
OL,14,Finto absolute poverty last year.
OL,16,FThey added: "We are supporting hard-
OL,17,Fworking families by raising the
OL,18,FNational Living Wage, cutting taxes
OL,19,Fand driving down inflation to help
OL,20,Ftheir money go further."
